sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note
    activate server
    server-->>browser: 201 Created (New note added)
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: User input and interaction to create a new note

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Updated JSON data with the new note
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: The browser updates the SPA to reflect the new note
